ALSO TONS OF STORAGE AND A  SHOWER THAT ITS NOT HOOKED UP ANYMORE IN LOWER LEVEL.. YOU WILL LOVE THE AWESOME YARD COMPLETE WITH A VINYL PRIVACY FENCE AND LARGE PATIO FOR ENTERTAINING PLUS A STORAGE SHED. THIS HOME ALSO HAS A TENANT WITH INCOME COMING IN, IF YOU ARE LOOKING TO GROW YOUR PORTFOLIO. This home is eligible for the 2-1 Buydown (reduce your interest rate)
